edu.nd.darts.cimon
Class EavesdropList

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.TimerList
      edu.nd.darts.cimon.EavesdropList

public class EavesdropList
extends TimerList

List of opportunistic periodic monitor requests for a specific metric, sorted by maximum allowed update period. Monitors in this list will be updated each time an updated value is made available due to another monitor. Extends TimerList to override functionality of insert() and pophead().

Author:
darts

popHead

public TimerNode popHead()
Description copied from class: TimerList
Pop node from head of list. If monitor has not reached end of duration, set next update time for node, and re-insert into list. If monitor has reached end of duration, remove from list.

Overrides:

popNode

public TimerNode popNode(TimerNode tnode,
                         int monitorId)
Method matching the functionality of popHead for nodes in interior of list. Needed for opportunistic list, since these nodes are iterated without reordering.

Parameters:
tnode - opportunistic monitor node which has just been updated
monitorId - monitor ID of tnode
Returns:
tnode if duration has expired, null otherwise
